The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 The chilli factor

London: The English women cricketers are preparing for its tour of India early next year by having chilli-eating competitions! 

Knowing well that they would have to make do with spicy Indian food when they tour the country in February for a quadrangular meet, coach Richard Bates encouraged his girls to go on a chilli eating spree. He was surprised by their enthusiastic response to the novel training method. 

 (PTI) 




